item.title: Prayer bpn6232 in Luganda
item.description: Ayi Mukama! Fuula omuvubuka ono omusanyufu, era osse emikisa Gyo ku kitonde kino ekinaku. Omuwe amagezi era omwongere amaanyi buli makya, era omukuumire mu kisiikirize ky’obukuumi Bwo, olwo alyoke ave ku bikyamu byonna yemalire mu kuweereza Enzikiriza Yo, Alungamye ababuze, akutembere abatalina mikisa, ayimbule abasibe, era azuukuse abatafaayo, olwo bonna bafune omukisa n’okukujukira, n’okukutendereza. Ggwe oli w’Amaanyi, Ayinza byonna. (Source category: ABAVUBUKA) (Bahaiprayers.net ID: 6232)
